{"data":[{"id":563781436,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4d5ac508d89d0be22389f1dacabd0a90","url_token":"virbianium","name":"而后 乃今培风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b5d0eb929c513a4b6cc65f1be8a8a3a1_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b5d0eb929c513a4b6cc65f1be8a8a3a1_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4d5ac508d89d0be22389f1dacabd0a90","user_type":"people","headline":"一个想成为理论物理学家，也知道自己可能在做梦但为之奋斗的青年。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":8,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563781436","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276229,"updated_time":1546280108,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e题主第一个问题很多人都回答了，我在这就不再赘述。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e回答第二个问题：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不是。他目前对自己能力的自信已经到了盲目的地步，在发表这文章之前他提的问题 \u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/306537777/answer/562859753\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？\u003c/a\u003e回答数已经破2K了，如果他看一下里面大多数回答，认真考虑自己的能力，就不会做出如此荒唐的行为。真正的天才从来不会将自己看的太高，他这种不顾他人劝告而一意孤行的人，如果继续走这条歧路，可能以后连庸才都说不上。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个年纪的人自视太高的情况常常会有，答主年纪和他也差不了几岁，很理解他这种渴望通过一个伟大的发现或者成就一夜成名的想法。唯一的不同是答主醒的更早，认清了自己的能力，选择一条不那么艰难，但是现实得多地多的路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e的确有很多人对他言辞太过尖锐，我只希望他不要因为太多人的指责和严厉的言辞失去信心，不要沉浸在这次惨重且广为人知的失败里面，也希望大家不要对他进行攻击，他只是个高中生，也许真的有错，但是那不是你们对他大肆冷嘲热讽的理由。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有梦想是好事，有宏伟的梦想更是无可厚非，任何人都渴望自己能做出一番惊天动地的成就，但是要找好路。\u003cb\u003e重要的不是路通向的山有多高，也不是路本身多平坦宽阔，甚至不是路旁的风景多么美丽，而是多年后回忆在这条路上的每一个脚印时，都会会心一笑。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"题主第一个问题很多人都回答了，我在这就不再赘述。回答第二个问题：不是。他目前对自己能力的自信已经到了盲目的地步，在发表这文章之前他提的问题 \u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/306537777/answer/562859753\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？\u003c/a\u003e回答数已经破2K了，如果他看一下里面大多数回…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=125\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment